    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[0]'
      value: we
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[1]'
      value: Roland, did you hear about Ralf... that makes 7 deaths this week, and
        the number is rising...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[2]'
      value: Well, you know how it is with this job, every day could be your last.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[3]'
      value: Roland, I'm serious. What would happen if you or I were next? Just because
        I'm strong doesn't mean I can just die.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[4]'
      value: Wow...don't worry, you know that won't happen, we're in this together.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[5]'
      value: Hmm... Roland, what if one day you were next? I could never forget myself...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[6]'
      value: No, no, don't talk nonsense. I would never leave you alone; that's the
        advantage of having a beautiful wife, much stronger than you.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[7]'
      value: Yes, yes, don't worry, I'll protect you, but maybe someday we could
        be more than just facility cleaners.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[8]'
      value: That's the spirit! Now it's almost time for my shift, so we should start
        heading out, don't you think?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[9]'
      value: Well, if you want... one day... we could go far away from here, you
        and I, escape this rotten city, but the people here need us... at least for
        now.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[10]'
      value: ....
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[11]'
      value: Roland...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[12]'
      value: mhmh?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[13]'
      value: If something ever happens to me... please don't blame yourself for anything
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'sentences.Array.data[14]'
      value: as sure as if something like that would happen
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8373581846860197092, guid: ecb75a9cd6ed46046981a46b53ffb670, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueSounds.Array.size
      value: 15
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
